snippet.title: Psionic Awake Trailer (DEMO free on itch )
snippet.description:
Steam page: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2236590/Psionic_Awake/
Play demo free on Itch:
https://indiecn.itch.io/psionic-awake
Join our discord: https://discord.gg/qcKabj2AAR
Psionic Awake is a Roguelike; Vampire like game . 
Collect resources during the day and defend against monsters at night. 
It emphasizes any combination of weapons, talents, treasures and partners.
